structure.unit: STATE UNIVERSITIES AND COLLEGES -- REGIONAL EDUCATION -- ARCHAEOLOGY

law.catch_line: Recognition of Area Health Education System.
law.text: The Area Health Education System in the Council on Postsecondary Education is hereby recognized.
law.history: Amended 1997 (1st Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 1, sec. 80, effective May 30, 1997. -- Created 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 20, sec. 5, effective July 15, 1980.
